20a%20lawyer%20or%20a%20billionaire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Boulos%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674cae3de45a68623a2753c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223270%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Boulos%20worked%20to%20boost%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20Michigan%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election.%3Cp%3EJeenah%20Moon%20for%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMassad%20Boulos%20helped%20Trump%20win%20Arab%20voters%20in%20Michigan.%20He's%20also%20Tiffany%20Trump's%20father-in-law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENews%20outlets%20have%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bbillionaire%26quot%3B%20and%20repeated%20Trump's%20description%20of%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Blawyer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20he%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20have%20a%20law%20license%2C%20and%20his%20company%20has%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20%24865%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMassad%20Boulos%2C%20who%20has%20been%20widely%20described%20as%20a%20billionaire%20and%20a%20lawyer%20and%20was%20recently%20named%20as%20one%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20advisors%20on%20Middle%20East%20affairs%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20neither%20a%20billionaire%20nor%20a%20licensed%20attorney%2C%20according%20to%20public%20records%20and%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoulos%20first%20entered%20the%20public%20eye%20in%202018%2C%20when%20his%20son%20Michael%20met%20Tiffany%20Trump%20at%20a%20club%20in%20Greece%20and%20the%20pair%20began%20dating.%20The%20couple%20married%20at%20Mar-A-Lago%20in%202022%2C%20making%20Massad%20Boulos%20Tiffany's%20father-in-law.%20He%20was%20credited%20in%20news%20stories%20with%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20Donald%20Trump's%202024%20electoral%20victory%2C%20helping%20peel%20Arab%20American%20voters%20away%20from%20Democrats%20in%20battlegrounds%20like%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Trump%20said%20Boulos%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsenior%20advisor%26quot%3B%20on%20Middle%20Eastern%20affairs%2C%20joining%20a%20team%20that%20includes%20Trump's%20longtime%20friend%20and%20supporter%20Steven%20Witkoff%2C%20his%20pick%20for%20ambassador%20to%20Israel%20Mike%20Huckabee%2C%20and%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20his%20nominee%20for%20secretary%20of%20state%2C%20who%20will%20shape%20US%20policy%20in%20the%20region.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Trump%20described%20Boulos%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Baccomplished%20lawyer%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20respected%20leader%20in%20the%20business%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Trump%20apparently%20inflated%20Boulos's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20Business%20Insider%20found%20no%20proof%20of%20Boulos's%20supposed%20billions.%20And%20while%20he%20may%20have%20attended%20law%20school%2C%20he%20hasn't%20passed%20a%20bar%20exam%20and%20can't%20practice%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258b98903-f1ab-4426-a221-4308a80531c6%5C%22%3ENo%20connection%20to%20a%20company%20that%20shares%20his%20last%20name%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20does%20control%20a%20truck%20dealership%20worth%20less%20than%20%241%20million%20in%20Nigeria%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClaims%20of%20the%20Boulos%20family's%20wealth%20first%20started%20circulating%20in%20English-language%20media%20in%202018%2C%20when%20Tiffany%20Trump's%20relationship%20with%20Michael%20Boulos%20became%20public.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2018%2F11%2F29%2Ftiffany-trumps-wealthy-new-boyfriend-grew-up-in-nigeria%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20family%20%26quot%3Bowns%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20conglomerate%26quot%3B%20and%20later%20mentioned%20Boulos%20Enterprises.%20Vanity%20Fair%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fstyle%2F2018%2F11%2Ftiffany-trumps-boyfriend-spent-thanksgiving-at-mar-a-lago%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eechoed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20description%20of%20the%20Boulos%20businesses%20as%20%26quot%3Bworth%20billions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20description%20that%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%202%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20said%20Massad%20Boulos%20built%20%26quot%3Bhis%20wealth%20in%20West%20Africa%26quot%3B%20and%20runs%20two%20companies%2C%20SCOA%20Nigeria%20and%20Boulos%20Enterprises.%20The%20Financial%20Times%20called%20him%20an%20%26quot%3Bauto%20tycoon%26quot%3B%20who%20leads%20both%20companies%2C%20while%20ABC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Ftrump-picks-daughter-tiffanys-father-law-massad-boulos%2Fstory%3Fid%3D116351766%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%26quot%3Bbillionaire%20businessman%26quot%3B%20who%20%26quot%3Bruns%20Boulos%20Enterprises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Massad%20Boulos%20doesn't%20run%20Boulos%20Enterprises%2C%20according%20to%20several%20former%20employees%20and%20its%20actual%20boss%2C%20Boulos%20Boulos.%20Boulos%20Enterprises%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Boulos%20Group%2C%20a%20holding%20company%20owned%20by%20a%20different%20group%20of%20Lebanese%20Nigerians%20with%20the%20same%20last%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20due-diligence%20report%20for%20Boulos%20Enterprises%20Ltd.%20created%20by%20Moody's%20Orbis%20database%20doesn't%20mention%20Massad%20Boulos.%20Archived%20copies%20of%20the%20Boulos%20Group%20website%20from%202016%20and%202018%20didn't%20mention%20him%2C%20either.%20And%20Elephant%20Africa%20Holding%2C%20a%20Mauritius%20company%20created%20by%20the%20Boulos%20Group%20to%20hold%20its%20paper%20businesses%2C%20also%20doesn't%20mention%20Massad%20in%20its%20corporate%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F12%2F12%2Fworld%2Fafrica%2Ftrump-massad-boulos-middle-east.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20Boulos's%20wealth%20and%20backstory%20into%20question%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20he%20previously%20misled%20one%20of%20its%20reporters%20by%20answering%20%26quot%3Byeah%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20accurate%20to%20call%20his%20company%20a%20multi-billion%20dollar%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20headlines%20in%20news%20outlets%2C%20BI%20couldn't%20find%20any%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20Massad%20Boulos%20is%20a%20billionaire.%20The%20company%20Massad%20Boulos%20actually%20does%20run%2C%20SCOA%20Nigeria%2C%20which%20has%20a%20subsidiary%20called%20SCOA%20Motors%2C%20is%20a%20penny%20stock.%20Its%20shares%20trade%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fngxgroup.com%2Fexchange%2Fdata%2Fcompany-profile%2F%3Fsymbol%3DSCOA%26directory%3Dcompanydirectory%26tdate%3D2024-12-05T00%3A00%3A00%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20two%20Nigerian%20naira%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20roughly%20a%20tenth%20of%20a%20US%20cent%2C%20making%20the%20entire%20business%20worth%20about%20%24865%2C000.%20That's%20not%20Billionaire's%20Row%20money%2C%20but%20it%20could%20buy%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstreeteasy.com%2Fbuilding%2F30_80-47-street-astoria%2F3a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20957-square-foot%20condo%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Queens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoclib.ngxgroup.com%2FFinancial_NewsDocs%2F42516_S_C_O_A__NIGERIA_PLC-_QUARTER_3_-_FINANCIAL_STATEMENT_FOR_2024_FINANCIAL_STATEMENTS_OCTOBER_2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20annual%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20partly%20printed%20in%20Comic%20Sans%2C%20is%20consistent%20with%20such%20a%20valuation.%20For%20its%20financial%20year%20ending%20September%2030%2C%20SCOA%20reported%20about%205.9%20billion%20naira%2C%20or%20%243.7%20million%2C%20in%20revenue%20and%20about%2025%20million%20naira%2C%20or%20%2415%2C562%2C%20in%20post-tax%20profits.%20The%20year%20before%2C%20when%20sales%20were%20weaker%2C%20SCOA%20lost%20about%20715%20million%20naira%2C%20or%20%24444%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20interviews%20with%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Boulos%20has%20said%20he%20didn't%20correct%20the%20record%20because%20he%20doesn't%20discuss%20his%20businesses.%20He%20also%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20value%20his%20family's%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20possible%20that%20Massad%20Boulos's%20family%20could%20have%20other%20sources%20of%20wealth.%20His%20wife%2C%20Sarah%20Fadoul%20Boulos%2C%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20another%20Lebanese%20businessman%20in%20Africa%2C%20Michel%20Zouhair%20Fadoul%2C%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffadoulgroup.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%3C%2Fa%3E%20boasts%20of%20a%20presence%20in%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%2010%20countries%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the961.com%2Flebanese-family-dynasties-africa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elisted%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20the%20most%20successful%20Lebanese%20businesses%20in%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20social%20media%2C%20Massad%20and%20his%20family%20seem%20to%20live%20large%2C%20posting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FByPlMO0nsTX%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20yacht%20floating%20off%20the%20southern%20coast%20of%20France%20and%20a%20ski%20run%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCYTy77FMpRh%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Alps%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20Massad%20Boulos%20has%20virtually%20no%20history%20of%20political%20giving%2C%20his%20son%20Michael%20made%20%24200%2C000%20in%20political%20contributions%20in%20two%20days%20in%202020.%20Michael%20was%20also%20reported%20to%20have%20proposed%20to%20Tiffany%20with%20a%20%241.2%20million%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20which%20he%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Ffemail%2Farticle-11426633%2FTiffany-Trump-upgraded-1-5-MILLION-engagement-ring-wedding-Michael-Boulos.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupgraded%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20to%20an%20even%20pricier%20piece%20by%20their%20wedding%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhone%20numbers%20listed%20for%20Massad%20Boulos%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20disconnected.%20Efforts%20to%20reach%20him%20through%20family%20members%20and%20political%20associates%20weren't%20successful.%20The%20Trump%20transition%20team%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d116c3e0-0465-41f8-9254-8c4309711c43%5C%22%3E'Is%20not%20now%2C%20and%20never%20has%20been%2C%20an%20attorney%20licensed%20to%20practice%20law'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20not%20clear%20that%20Massad%20Boulos%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Blawyer%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20described%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20news%20outlets%20say%20that%20Boulos%20has%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Houston.%20But%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20University%20of%20Houston%20system%20said%20that's%20not%20correct%3B%20Boulos%20has%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20%26quot%3Bgeneral%20business%26quot%3B%20from%20one%20of%20its%20smaller%20schools%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Houston-Downtown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202015%20interview%20on%20Nigerian%20TV%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeDcEXrMDqug%262m00s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESarah%20Boulos%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20her%20husband%20%26quot%3Bgraduated%20as%20a%20lawyer%20from%20Thurgood%20Marshall%20School%2C%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20Texas%20Southern%20University%2C%20before%20they%20moved%20to%20Nigeria.%20Massad%20Boulos%20also%20listed%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20school%20on%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%20before%20the%20profile%20went%20offline%2C%20according%20to%20information%20saved%20in%20the%20contact%20database%20Rocketreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%20Southern%20officials%20didn't%20respond%20to%20several%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20graduating%20from%20law%20school%20doesn't%20make%20someone%20a%20lawyer.%20Nahdiah%20Hoang%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Texas%20Board%20of%20Law%20Examiners%2C%20said%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Boulos%20applied%20to%20take%20the%20July%201996%20bar%20exam%2C%20but%20he%20either%20didn't%20take%20it%20or%20didn't%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokeswoman%20for%20the%20Texas%20Bar%20said%20Boulos%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20now%2C%20and%20never%20has%20been%2C%20an%20attorney%20licensed%20to%20practice%20law%20in%20Texas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20also%20checked%20bar%20records%20for%20DC%20and%2047%20other%20states%20%E2%80%94%20covering%2099%25%20of%20the%20US%20population%20%E2%80%94%20and%20found%20Boulos%20wasn't%20registered%20as%20a%20lawyer%20in%20any%20of%20those%20states%2C%20either.%20(BI%20was%20unable%20to%20confirm%20if%20Boulos%20was%20registered%20to%20practice%20law%20in%20Alaska%20or%20South%20Dakota.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EL'Orient%20Le%20Jour%2C%20a%20Lebanese%20newspaper%2C%20reported%20that%20Boulos%20is%20also%20a%20citizen%20of%20Lebanon%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20France.%20There's%20no%20public%20evidence%20that%20Boulos%20is%20licensed%20as%20a%20lawyer%20in%20any%20of%20those%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20not%20listed%20in%20the%20directories%20for%20the%2011%20largest%20French%20bar%20associations%2C%20which%20cover%20two-thirds%20of%20French%20lawyers.%20Lawyers%20in%20Lebanon%20must%20be%20registered%20with%20one%20of%20two%20bar%20associations%3B%20one%20of%20them%2C%20the%20Beirut%20Bar%20Association%2C%20said%20Boulos%20wasn't%20in%20its%20database%2C%20and%20the%20other%20didn't%20respond%20to%20repeated%20inquiries.%20The%20Nigerian%20Bar%20Association%20and%20the%20country's%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20maintains%20its%20registry%20of%20lawyers%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20emails%20about%20whether%20Boulos%20was%20an%20attorney.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3ENarimes%20Parakul%20contributed%20reporting.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h