for%20foreign%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Department%20for%20Promotion%20of%20Industry%20and%20Internal%20Trade%20or%20DPIIT%20showed%20that%20the%20cumulative%20amount%20of%20FDI%2C%20including%20equity%2C%20reinvested%20earnings%20and%20other%20capital%2C%20stood%20at%20USD%201%2C033.40%20billion%20(or%20%241%20trillion)%20between%20April%202000%20and%20September%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20perspective%20of%20just%20how%20gigantic%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20really%20is%2C%20let's%20take%20this%20simple%20example%20-%20If%20a%20person%20was%20to%20earn%20one%20dollar%20(Rs.%2084)%20per%20second%20(i.e.%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20in%20trillion%20seconds)%20-%20then%20it%20would%20take%20the%20person%2011.5%20days%20to%20earn%20a%20million%20dollars.%20But%20here's%20where%20is%20gets%20interesting.%20Continuing%20to%20earn%20a%20dollar%20a%20second%2C%20it%20would%20take%20the%20person%2031.7%20years%20to%20reach%20the%20billion-dollar%20mark%2C%20and%20a%20staggering%2031%2C709%20years%20to%20reach%20the%20trillion-dollar%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20thought-provoking%20way%20to%20look%20at%20this%20is%20that%20India%2C%20which%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20global%20economy%2C%20has%20an%20overall%20GDP%20of%20around%20%243.89%20trillion%20in%202024.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20around%20%242%20trillion%20in%202014.%20Now%20compare%20that%20to%20the%20FDI%20inflow%20of%20%241%20trillion%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESOURCE%20OF%20THE%20FDI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20where%20did%20all%20this%20investment%20come%20from%3F%20Which%20are%20the%20countries%20from%20which%20these%20investments%20flowed%20in%3F%20One%20might%20assume%20that%20the%20top%20spot%20would%20be%20either%20the%20US%2C%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20or%20perhaps%20China%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20globally.%20But%20it's%20neither.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20which%20has%20contributed%20the%20most%20in%20terms%20of%20FDI%20in%20India%20during%20this%20period%20is%20Mauritius%20-%20a%20massive%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20FDI%20inflows%20came%20via%20this%20route.%20Mauritius%20was%20closely%20followed%20by%20Singapore%20at%2024%20per%20cent.%20The%20United%20States%20of%20America%20came%20a%20distant%20third%20with%2010%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20countries%20which%20have%20invested%20significantly%20in%20India%20include%20The%20Netherlands%20at%207%20per%20cent%2C%20Japan%20at%206%20per%20cent%2C%20The%20UK%20at%205%20per%20cent%2C%20UAE%20at%203%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20the%20Cayman%20Islands%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Cyprus%20all%20accounting%20for%202%20per%20cent%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESECTORS%20WHICH%20SAW%20BIG%20INVESTMENT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20which%20saw%20the%20highest%20investment%20was%20the%20services%20and%20allied%20sector.%20There%20was%20significant%20investment%20in%20computer%20software%20and%20hardware%2C%20telecommunications%2C%20trading%2C%20construction%2C%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20automobile%2C%20chemicals%2C%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFDI%20INFLOWS%20ON%20THE%20RISE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201%2C033%20billion%20dollars%2C%20USD%20667.4%20billion%20came%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20between%202014%20and%202024%20showing%20a%20119%20per%20cent%20uptick%20in%20investment%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20decade.%20The%20data%20also%20revealed%20that%20FDI%20inflows%20have%20come%20for%20nearly%2060%20sectors%20across%2031%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20attract%20more%20investment%20over%20time%2C%20India%20has%20also%20made%20its%20investment%20policies%20liberal%20and%20lucrative.%20Reforms%20have%20resulted%20in%20most%20sectors%2C%20barring%20ones%20of%20strategic%20importance%2C%20see%20100%20per%20cent%20FDI%20under%20the%20automatic%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20impetus%20to%20the%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%2C%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20has%20seen%20a%2069%20per%20cent%20rise%20in%20FDI%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20prior%20ten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHICH%20SECTORS%20ARE%20OPEN%20AND%20WHAT%20IS%20THE%20PROCEDURE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFDI%20is%20allowed%20through%20the%20automatic%20route%20in%20most%20of%20the%20sectors%2C%20while%20in%20areas%20like%20telecom%2C%20media%2C%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20insurance%2C%20government%20approval%20is%20required%20for%20foreign%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20government%20approval%20route%2C%20a%20foreign%20investor%20has%20to%20get%20a%20prior%20nod%20from%20the%20ministry%20or%20department%20concerned%2C%20whereas%2C%20under%20the%20automatic%20route%2C%20an%20overseas%20investor%20is%20only%20required%20to%20inform%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20after%20the%20investment%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20FDI%20is%20prohibited%20in%20some%20sectors.%20They%20are%20lottery%2C%20gambling%20and%20betting%2C%20chit%20funds%2C%20Nidhi%20company%2C%20real%20estate%20business%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20of%20cigars%2C%20cheroots%2C%20cigarillos%20and%20cigarettes%20using%20tobacco.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734039060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F5hg5edjc_pm-modi-make-in-india-pmo-website_625x300_13_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findias-fdi-crosses-1-000-billion-since-turn-of-century-biggest-investor-is-7235677%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20week%20India%20crossed%20a%20major%20milestone%20as%20a%20top%20global%20investment%20destination.%20Latest%20data%20reveals%20that%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investment%20into%20I