cial%20wrote%20to%20managers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal%2C%20which%20said%20that%20Netflix%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20curb%20usage%20of%20the%20full%20year%20of%20leave%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20employees%2C%20taking%20more%20than%206%20months%20of%20parental%20leave%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bwidely%20understood%20to%20be%20an%20unwise%20career%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Journal%20reported.%20A%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20US%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20averaged%206.3%20months%20of%20parental%20leave%2C%20and%20employees%20outside%20the%20country%20averaged%207.5%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BEmployees%20have%20the%20freedom%2C%20flexibility%20and%20responsibility%20to%20determine%20what%20is%20best%20for%20them%20and%20their%20family.%20Our%20parental%20leave%20policy%20has%20always%20been%20to%20'take%20care%20of%20your%20child%20and%20yourself.'%26quot%3B%20Sergio%20Ezama%2C%20Netflix's%20chief%20talent%20officer%2C%20said%20the%20company%20has%20%26quot%3Bnot%20pulled%20back%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20parental%20leave%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20implemented%20a%20limit%20of%20%24300%20in%20company%20swag%20such%20as%20coffee%20mugs%20or%20sweatshirts%20per%20year%20that%20each%20employee%20can%20order%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20streamer%20has%20asked%20managers%20to%20tighten%20the%20purse%20strings%20on%20compensation.%20It%20previously%20let%20them%20pay%20above%20market%20rates%20to%20attract%20and%20retain%20talent%3B%20now%2C%20managers%20are%20asked%20to%20ensure%20salaries%20stay%20within%2050%25%20to%2095%25%20of%20employees'%20peers%2C%20per%20the%20Journal%2C%20citing%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-new-culture-memo-keeper-test-changes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2