A%20social%20worker%20in%20Manipur%20whose%20non-profit%20work%20was%20billed%20as%20a%20success%20story%20in%20helping%20youth%20and%20women%20in%20the%20border%20state%20affected%20by%20gun%20violence%2C%20has%20run%20into%20a%20huge%20controversy%20over%20his%20comments%20in%20a%20YouTube%20interview%20in%20which%20he%20was%20heard%20talking%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bneed%20for%20escalating%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20%26quot%3Balive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamkhojang%20Misao%20(aka%20Misao%20Hejang%20Hangmi%20aka%20Hejang%20Misao)%2C%20founder%20director%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Social%20And%20Institutional%20Development%20for%20Empowerment%20(InSIDE-North%20East)%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20YouTube%20channel%20'Nampi%20Media%20Jampilal'%20said%20the%20struggle%20for%20a%20separate%20land%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%20his%20forefathers'%20time%2C%20and%20despite%20having%20multiple%20factions%20of%20insurgents%20with%20numerous%20different%20demands%2C%20all%20of%20them%20finally%20managed%20to%20agree%20on%20one%20issue%20-%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20separate%20administration%20movement%20has%20reduced%20now.%20We%20will%20not%20get%20this%20chance%20anymore%2C%20and%20such%20an%20opportunity%20will%20not%20come%20again.%20We%20should%20use%20this%20moment%20to%20create%20an%20even%20more%20chaotic%20situation%2C%20so%20that%20anyone%20who%20sees%20us%20will%20say%20we%20can%20never%20live%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misao%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20distinct%20tribes%20collectively%20known%20as%20Kuki%2C%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20in%20his%20dialect%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20which%20was%20translated%20and%20corroborated%20by%20three%20sources%20from%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20for%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20the%20armed%20groups%20have%20come%20together%20on%20one%20demand.%20This%20is%20a%20work%20of%20God.%20But%20the%20Meiteis%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20us%20a%20separate%20administration.%20SoO%20groups%20also%20signed%20that%20Manipur%20territorial%20integrity%20won't%20be%20harmed.%20But%20God's%20plan%20seems%20to%20be%20about%20giving%20the%20Kukis%20a%20nation%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20it%20is%20there.%20If%20there%20was%20no%20violence%2C%20we%20would%20not%20have%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20demand%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misao%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20Kuki-Zo%20militant%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20the%20controversial%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fend-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-with-all-kuki-zo-insurgent-groups-manipur-assembly-in-unanimous-resolution-5150821%5C%22%3Ewhich%20lapsed%20in%20February%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20clauses%20in%20the%20SoO%20agreement%20says%20Manipur's%20territorial%20integrity%20will%20not%20be%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalls%20to%20the%20phone%20numbers%20mentioned%20on%20InSIDE-North%20East's%20website%20went%20unanswered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F84hdk5qg_manipur-violence_625x300_03_March_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20people%20in%20the%20social%20service%20sector%20who%20was%20selected%20to%20meet%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20in%20January%202020.%20He%20highlighted%20InSIDE-North%20East's%20'Gun2Pen'%20programme%20--%20among%20many%20other%20projects%20-%20which%20the%20non-profit%20said%20helped%20over%205%2C000%20young%20people%20find%20the%20right%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20God's%20work...%20this%20indicates%20God%20has%20a%20plan%20for%20us.%20The%20buffer%20zone%20is%20the%20evidence%20of%20the%20separation.%20Despite%20all%20these%20gains%2C%20and%20God's%20help%2C%20it%20seems%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20use%20the%20opportunity.%20The%20Meiteis%20started%20it%2C%20burnt%20our%20houses%2C%20killed%20our%20people%2C%20paraded%20women%20naked%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Misao%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20Any%20Kuki%20Tribe%20(AKT)%20that%20was%20added%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes'%20list%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20have%20created%20the%20situation%2C%20how%20do%20we%20escalate%20it%20more%20and%20more%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20alive%2C%20then%20our%20demand%20will%20be%20seriously%20considered%3F%20Now%2C%20the%20separate%20administration%20demand's%20momentum%20is%20dying%20slowly.%20Even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20parliament%20says%20normalcy%20has%20come%20in%20Manipur.%20Schools%20are%20running%2C%20markets%20are%20running%2C%20government%20offices%20are%20also%20running%2C%20those%20who%20are%20going%20to%20grant%20us%20separate%20administration%20themselves%20say%20normalcy%20has%20returned%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misao%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20don't%20agree%20with%20the%20claim%20by%20the%20government%20that%20normalcy%20has%20returned%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20already%20declared%20normalcy.%20So%2C%20in%20a%20place%20where%20there%20is%20normalcy%2C%20who%20is%20going%20to%20take%20up%20our%20issues%3F%20When%20the%20government%20in%20parliament%20says%20there%20is%20normalcy%2C%20we%20need%20to%20do%20something%20to%20show%20evidence%20that%20there%20is%20no%20normalcy.%20That's%20what's%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fevuvh79o_moreh-assam-rifles_625x300_11_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20on%20the%20central%20government's%20non-profit%20organisation%20(NPO)%20database%20'Darpan'%20shows%20Mr%20Misao%20registered%20the%20Integrated%20Social%20And%20Institutional%20Development%20for%20Empowerment%20in%20February%202013%20in%20Manipur's%20Kangpokpi%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20database%20contains%20unique%20identity%20numbers%20of%20NPOs.%20This%20unique%20ID%20number%20is%20mandatory%20if%20an%20NPO%20wants%20to%20take%20funds%20from%20government%20departments%20and%20ministries.%20Mr%20Misao's%20NPO%20has%20been%20allotted%20a%20unique%20identity%20number%20-%20MN%2F2017%2F0177675%20-%20which%20it%20can%20use%20to%20apply%20for%20grants%20from%20government%20departments%20and%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20situation.%20Whether%20armed%20groups%20or%20civil%20society%20groups%20or%20individuals%2C%20we%20have%20to%20introspect%2C%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20situation%20again%20as%20there%20is%20no%20complete%20normalcy%20yet.%20The%20world%20should%20know%20there%20will%20be%20no%20peace%20in%20Manipur%20without%20a%20solution.%20For%20leaders%20of%20the%20world%20and%20India%20to%20see%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20something%20so%20that%20they%20will%20know%20that%20Manipur%20needs%20a%20solution%20for%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20social%20worker%20from%20Kangpokpi%20district%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20blamed%20leaders%20for%20the%20weakening%20of%20the%20resolve%20to%20demand%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20If%20God%20has%20shown%20us%20the%20path%2C%20the%20leaders%20should%20have%20guided%20the%20public%20forward...%20There%20was%20a%20guy%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20C%20Singson%2C%20who%20asked%20the%20Indian%20interlocutor%20in%20Bangkok%20during%20the%20Naga%20talks%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Kuki%20issue%20never%20brought%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20interlocutor%20replied%20Kukis%20have%20never%20been%20an%20issue%2C%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20discuss%20about%20them.%20However%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20have%20with%20their%20actions%20against%20the%20Kukis%2C%20who%20never%20really%20had%20any%20grievances%2C%20have%20created%20a%20situation%20which%20has%20made%20the%20Indian%20government%20realise%20the%20Kukis%20have%20an%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20whole%20world%20has%20now%20recognised%20the%20Kukis'%20problem.%20That%20problem%20has%20to%20be%20escalated%20more%20and%20more.%20If%20that%20problem%20is%20not%20escalated%2C%20then%20the%20demand%20we%20are%20putting%20forward%20is%20not%20politically%20strong%20and%20reasonable.%20The%20Meiteis%20have%20made%20us%20politically%20strong.%20But%20today%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20take%20it%20forward.%20That's%20very%20unfortunate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvkl1bcig_churachandpur_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20villages%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20the%20hills%20surrounding%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20valley.%20The%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20killed%20over%20250%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%