0Asian%20Development%20Bank%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finance%20Department%20Sought%20Verifiable%20Data%20For%20AAP's%20Women%20Scheme%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20monthly%20financial%20aid%20for%20women%20in%20Delhi%20announced%20by%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20without%20solid%20funding%20source%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20have%20alleged%2C%20and%20have%20termed%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20election%20promise%20an%20attempt%20to%20mislead%20women%20voters%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20election%20scheduled%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20announcement%20to%20raise%20financial%20aid%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20Rs%202%2C100%20if%20the%20AAP%20is%20voted%20to%20power%20again%20in%20Delhi%20has%20attracted%20criticism%20from%20the%20ruling%20party's%20rivals%20over%20its%20funding%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Mahila%20Samman%20Yojna'%20was%20first%20proposed%20by%20the%20women%20and%20child%20development%20department%20to%20the%20finance%20department%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20department%20raised%20concern%20over%20the%20funding%20source%20and%20advised%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20draft%20to%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20without%20enough%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContours%20of%20the%20proposed%20scheme%20%5Bis%5D%20unclear%3B%20demanding%20more%20detailing%20and%20firming%20up%20of%20timelines%20to%20enable%20efficient%20and%20transparent%20spending%20of%20Rs%204%2C560%20crore%20annually.%20It%20is%20advised%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20draft%20cabinet%20note%20before%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20till%20a%20concrete%20scheme%20with%20verifiable%20data%20and%20roadmap%20is%20prepared%20for%20consideration%20by%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20finance%20department%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20announced%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20has%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20Delhi%20cabinet%2C%20leading%20to%20enhancement%20of%20the%20monthly%20amount%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%202%2C100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20since%20the%20election%20dates%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20the%20money%20transfers%20can't%20be%20done%20now%3B%20however%2C%20the%20registration%20process%20for%20availing%20benefits%20under%20the%20scheme%20will%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20avail%20this%20benefit%2C%20women%20will%20need%20to%20get%20themselves%20registered%20and%20once%20done%2C%20the%20amount%20will%20be%20directly%20transferred%20to%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20is%20contesting%20the%20Delhi%20election%20solo%20and%20have%20ruled%20out%20any%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Congress%20chief%20Devender%20Yadav%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20latest%20promise%20to%20give%20Rs%202%2C100%20per%20month%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bmothers%20and%20sisters%26quot%3B%20of%20Delhi%20was%20yet%20another%20false%20promise%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20honour%20his%20previous%20promise%20of%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20every%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20had%20stopped%20widow%20pension%20and%20the%20Ladli%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20BJP%20president%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20questioned%20why%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20promised%20Mahila%20Samman%20Rashi%20before%20the%20assembly%20election%2C%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20even%20after%20two%20years%20in%20power.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBefore%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20collected%20forms%20from%20women%20in%20Delhi%20and%20promised%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20starting%20September.%20However%2C%20no%20funds%20have%20been%20distributed%20to%20date%2C%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis