5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aarti%20didn't%20answer%20her%20partner's%20phone%20calls%20for%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20Ram%20Milan%20got%20worried.%20He%20dialed%20his%20sister-in-law%20and%20requested%20her%20to%20check%20on%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sister-in-law%20found%20the%20house%20locked%20from%20inside.%20The%20smell%20coming%20from%20the%20house%20was%20too%20strong%20to%20be%20ignored.%20It%20smelled%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20flew%20back%20to%20Gorakhpur%20on%20December%208.%20I%20saw%20my%20wife's%20body%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ram%20Milan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20informed%20the%20police%20who%20sprang%20into%20action%20and%20sent%20the%20body%20for%20postmortem.%20The%20boy%20was%20found%20sitting%20near%20a%20pond%20at%20a%20nearby%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20boy%20informed%20the%20police%20that%20his%20mother%20died%20due%20to%20a%20fall.%20He%20panicked%20and%20fled%20the%20house%20and%20wandered%20for%20four%20days%2C%20Aman%20told%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20investigation%20raised%20questions.%20Police%20found%20bloodstains%20at%20two%20different%20spots%2C%20indicating%20the%20body%20was%20dragged.%20They%20also%20recovered%20cash%20from%20the%20teenager's%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20neighbours%2C%20Aman%20was%20an%20addict.%20He%20would%20take%20up%20money%20from%20his%20mother%20in%20the%20name%20of%20coaching%20but%20would%20spend%20it%20on%20alcohol%20and%20drugs.%20Reportedly%2C%20the%20school%20too%20had%20complaints%20against%20Aman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20boy%20confessed%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20that%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20December%203%2C%20his%20mother%20asked%20him%20to%20go%20to%20school.%20When%20he%20refused%2C%20a%20dispute%20over%20money%20ensued%2C%20and%20his%20mother%20threw%20cash%20at%20him%20in%20frustration%2C%26quot%3B%20Superintendent%