ween%2020%20and%2030%20tonnes%20annually%2C%20mostly%20sourced%20from%20Shekhpur%20and%20neighbouring%20villages.%20These%20villagers%20were%20traditionally%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20lentils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20sale%20of%20fresh%20flowers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20lucrative%20enough%3B%20if%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sell%20them%2C%20the%20flowers%20would%20either%20be%20brought%20back%20home%20or%20discarded%20into%20the%20river.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328701%2Fpunjab-farmer-starts-floriculture-exotic-flowers-help-earn-more-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENishad%20convinced%20the%20farmers%20to%20grow%20these%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sell%20them%20to%20him.%20With%20his%20encouragement%2C%20the%20villagers%20took%20floriculture%20more%20seriously%20and%20now%20grow%20seven%20different%20varieties%20%E2%80%94%20Nishad%20purchases%20their%20entire%20harvest.%20The%20growers%20are%20paid%20promptly%20and%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20travel%2015%20km%20to%20the%20nearest%20%3Cem%3Emandi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20Nishad%20switched%20to%20farming%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20grow%20butterfly%20pea%20flowers%20instead%20of%20traditional%20crops.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-3-1733937411-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388809%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20Nishad%20switched%20to%20farming%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20grow%20butterfly%20pea%20flowers%20instead%20of%20traditional%20crops.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Nishad%20started%20with%20butterfly%20peas%20and%20has%20since%20expanded%20his%20product%20line%20to%20include%20rose%2C%20hibiscus%2C%20marigold%2C%20calendula%2C%20lemongrass%2C%20spearmint%2C%20tulsi%2C%20jasmine%2C%20chamomile%2C%20and%20ginger%20%E2%80%94%20all%20used%20for%20making%20teas%2C%20syrups%2C%20or%20preserves.%20%E2%80%9CI%20earn%20around%20a%20lakh%20rupees%20a%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishad%2C%20with%20a%20turnover%20ranging%20between%2020%20to%2030%20tonnes%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20established%20a%20small%20centre%20outside%20the%20village%20where%20farmers%20from%20the%20nearby%20area%20come%20to%20sell%20their%20harvested%20flowers%20twice%20a%20day%20%E2%80%94%20once%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20once%20in%20the%20evening.%20These%20fresh%20flowers%20are%20dehydrated%20within%2012%20to%2015%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20solar%20dryers%20was%20a%20key%20turning%20point%20in%20Nishad%E2%80%99s%20business%20venture.%20Initially%2C%20he%20dried%20flowers%20in%20an%20open%20environment%2C%20exposed%20to%20dust%2C%20bird%20droppings%2C%20and%20unpredictable%20weather%20conditions%2C%20which%20could%20damage%20the%20product.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20invested%20in%20a%20solar%20dryer%20costing%20Rs%2060%2C000%2C%20which%20not%20only%20accelerated%20the%20dehydration%20process%20but%20also%20ensured%20that%20the%20product%20remained%20pure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%3A%20A%20game-changer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solar%20dryer%2C%20consisting%20of%20trays%20placed%20on%20a%20metal%20stand%20under%20a%20roof%20of%20polycarbonate%20sheets%20with%20a%20total%20area%20of%20about%20five%20square%20metres%2C%20is%20particularly%20valuable%20during%20the%20monsoon%20when%20flowers%20typically%20get%20wasted.%20With%20this%20setup%2C%20Nishad%20can%20dry%20two%20batches%20of%20flowers%20per%20day%2C%20compared%20to%20just%20one%20using%20open-air%20drying%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325711%2Findore-engineer-foldable-solar-dryers-to-help-farmers-boost-income-tomato-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%20have%20been%20a%20game-changer%20for%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishad.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20ensure%20the%20highest%20quality%20products%20by%20preventing%20dust%2C%20preserving%20colour%20and%20texture%2C%20protecting%20against%20rain%2C%20and%20maintaining%20overall%20product%20quality%2C%20which%20allows%20farmers%20to%20command%20premium%20prices%20in%20the%20market.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20705px)%20100vw%2C%20705px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishad-in-front-of-the-new-solar-dryer-he-has-fabricated_11zon-1733937512.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22705%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nishad%20fabricated%20a%20new%20solar%20dryer%20to%20dehydrate%20local%20flowers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishad-in-front-of-the-new-solar-dryer-he-has-fabricated_11zon-1733937512.jpg%20705w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FNishad-in-front-of-the-new-solar-dryer-he-has-fabricated_11zon-1733937512-300x222.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F