20flower%20exports%20due%20to%20its%20wide%20availability%20of%20various%20plant%20species.%20Dried%20flowers%20are%20exported%20to%20the%20USA%2C%20Japan%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20The%20export%20industry%20for%20dried%20flowers%20and%20plants%20from%20India%20is%20valued%20at%20around%20Rs%20100%20crore%20annually%2C%20with%20over%20500%20varieties%20being%20shipped%20to%2020%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNishad%E2%80%99s%20success%20has%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20numerous%20farmers%20from%20his%20region%2C%20leading%20over%20100%20farmers%20to%20collaborate%20by%20supplying%20raw%20materials%2C%20thereby%20improving%20their%20livelihoods.%20His%20story%20inspires%20other%20farmers%20to%20leverage%20the%20locally%20available%20farm%20produce%2C%20cater%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20food%20loss%2Fspoilage%2C%20and%20integrate%20innovative%20clean-energy-powered%20livelihood%20technology%20to%20improve%20their%20incomes%20via%20value%20addition%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Divya%20Gaur%2C%20programme%20lead%2C%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiring%20farmers%20to%20embrace%20solar%20drying%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolar%20dryers%20enable%20farmers%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eefficiently%20dry%20perishable%20commodities%20like%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20flowers%2C%20and%20herbs.%20These%20dryers%20ensure%20the%20highest%20quality%20products%20by%20preventing%20dust%2C%20preserving%20colour%20and%20texture%2C%20protecting%20against%20rain%2C%20and%20maintaining%20overall%20product%20quality%2C%20which%20allows%20farmers%20to%20command%20premium%20prices%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20CEEW%20e