ute%2C%20Michael%20Kugelman%2C%20said%20the%20rejection%20of%20the%20loan%20%26quot%3Bis%20more%20than%20symbolic.%20It%20is%20strategic%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20this%20really%20was%20an%20initiative%20that%20US%20officials%20saw%20as%20a%20way%20to%20meaningfully%20counter%20China's%20own%20activities%20in%20terms%20of%20infrastructure%20investments%20in%20the%20broader%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%24553%20million%20loan%20by%20the%20US%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation%20was%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20infrastructure%20investment%20in%20Asia%20by%20the%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Corporation%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20was%20set%20up%20in%202019%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20counter%20the%20Chinese%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%20This%20port%20project%20was%20to%20be%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bfocused%20effort%20by%20Washington%20and%20New%20Delhi%20to%20counter%20Beijing's%20rising%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20port%20terminal%20in%20Colombo%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20ports%20in%20South%20Asia%20and%20is%20an%20important%20node%20to%20key%20international%20shipping%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20under%20the%20Rajapaksas%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20getting%20close%20to%20the%20Chinese%2C%20as%20massive%20loans%20and%20investment%20in%20infrastructure%20building%20took%20place%20on%20the%20island.%20The%20Chinese%20also%20have%20their%20own%20port%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2011%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20informed%20the%20bourses%20in%20an%20exchange%20filing%20that%20they%20would%20forgo%20the%20loan%20by%20the%20US%20Corporation%20and%20fund%20the%20port%20project%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20Founder%20and%20Chairman%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Washingt