2%3Cp%3EIndia's%2018-year-old%20grandmaster%20Gukesh%20Dommaraju%20scripted%20history%20on%20Thursday%20as%20he%20beat%20China's%20Ding%20Liren%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship%202024%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest-ever%20world%20champion.%20Not%20only%20was%20he%20the%20youngest%2C%20Gukesh%20also%20became%20the%20first-ever%20teenager%20to%20achieve%20this%20feat.%20Gukesh%20follows%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20Indian%20chess%20legend%20Viswanathan%20Anand%2C%20becoming%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20crown%20and%20the%20first%20since%202012.%20The%2014th%20and%20final%20match%20seemed%20to%20head%20towards%20a%20draw%2C%20but%20a%20late%20blunder%20by%20Ding%20Liren%20to%20sacrifice%20his%20rook%20handed%20Gukesh%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20triumph%2C%20Gukesh%20was%20elated%20after%20his%20decade-long%20dream%20turned%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20dreaming%20this%20moment%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20realised%20the%20dream%20(and%20made%20it)%20into%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20soft-spoken%20Chennai-lad%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20historic%20triumph%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20bit%20emotional%20because%20I%20was%20not%20expecting%20to%20win.%20But%20then%20I%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20press%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20chess%20player%20wants%20to%20live%20this%20dream.%20I%20am%20living%20my%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gukesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20his%20opponent%2C%20Gukesh%20added%26quot%3BTo%20me%20Ding%20is%20a%20real%20world%20champion.%20He%20fought%20like%20a%20true%20champion%20and%20I'm%20sorry%20for%20Ding%20and%20team.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20my%20opponent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20his%20parents'%20contributions%2C%20Gukesh%20revealed%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20dream%20of%20winning%20world%20chess%20championship%20is%20bigger%20for%20them%20than%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-olk-copy-source%3D%5C%22MessageBody%5C%22%3EBy%20beating%20Ding%2C%20Gukesh%20is%20the%2018th%20World%20Champion%20in%20the%20over%20century-long%20history%20of%20chess%20and%20the%20youngest%20after%20beating%20Garry%20Kasparov's%20record%20of%20winning%20the%20title%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021%20and%20heralding%20the%20arrival%20of%20a%20new%20king%20on%20the%20chess%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGukesh%20is%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship%20title%2C%20claiming%20the%20title%20in%20just%20over%20a%20decade%20after%20five-time%20Champion%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20had%20lost%20the%20title%20to%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20of%20Norway%20in%20Chennai%20in%202013.%20Carlsen%20has%20abdicated%20the%20crown%20in%202023%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20Ding%20to%20beat%20Ian%20Nepomniachtchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20battled%20it%20out%20for%2013%20games%20over%20three%20weeks%2C%20Ding%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20rapid%20and%20blitz%20tiebreakers%20as%20had%20effectively%20countered%20the%20aggressive%20tactics%20of%20the%20young%20Indian%20challenger%20to%20steer%20the%20game%20towards%20a%20drawish%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2032-year-old%20China%20made%20a%20sensational%20blunder%20when%20he%20moved%20his%20rook%2C%20leading%20it%20to%20be%20trapped%20and%20lose%20the%20game%20as%20Gukesh%20had%20an%20extra%20pawn%20in%20the%20king%20pawn%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGukesh%20nearly%20leapt%20out%20of%20his%20chair%2C%20took%20a%20pause%2C%20settled%20his%20nerves%2C%20claimed%20the%20rook%20sealed%20the%20victory%20and%20claimed%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20IANS%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734012240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9h59s8ec_gukesh_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fwasnt-expecting-to-win-emotio