ld-championship-title-is-viral-video-7233145%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20launches%20women-only%20bike%20taxi%20service%20'Moto%20Women'%20in%20Bengaluru%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734010222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fuber-launches-women-only-bike-taxi-service-moto-women-in-bengaluru-124121200998_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rolled%20out%20first%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Uber%20has%20plans%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20in%20other%20top%20cities%20such%20as%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVery%20Welcome%20Idea%26quot%3B%3A%20Former%20Chief%20Justice%20UU%20Lalit%20On%20Constitution%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20UU%20Lalit%20has%20said%20the%20planned%20debate%20on%20the%20Constitution%20in%20parliament%20%26quot%3Bcertainly%20has%20good%20features%20about%20it%26quot%3B.%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Lalit%20said%20every%20now%20and%20then%2C%20it%20is%20good%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20constitutional%20aspirations%2C%20goals%20and%20what%20exactly%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20till%20now%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20can't%20be%20anything%20better%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parliamentarians%20quite%20periodically%20keep%20on%20taking%20stock%20of%20situations%20as%20to%20where%20exactly%20do%20we%20stand%2C%20how%20far%20have%20we%20come%2C%20whether%20there%20are%20any%20provisions%20which%20require%20any%20amendment%20or%20whether%20any%20amendments%20which%20had%20been%20effected%20up%20till%20now%2C%20whether%20those%20amendments%20need%20any%20kind%20of%20fresh%20reading.%20So%20therefore%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20introspection%20is%20something%20which%20is%20always%20welcome%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Lalit%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20the%20parliamentarians%20wish%20to%20do%20that%20kind%20of%20introspection%20on%20the%20achievements%20on%20the%20constitutional%20front%2C%20then%20it%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20welcome%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20how%20India's%20Constitution%20has%20fared%20so%20far%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Lali%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bfared%20very%2C%20very%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20the%20judicial%20interpretation%20also%20helped%20us.%20In%20the%20initial%20case%2C%20the%20first%20case%2C%20which%20was%20AK%20Gopalan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20arguments%20which%20were%20advanced%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20petitioner%20was%20that%20when%20you%20consider%20and%20interpret%20the%20expression%20except%20in%20accordance%20with%20procedure%20established%20by%20law%20in%20Article%2021%2C%20do%20you%20simply%20go%20by%20the%20procedure%20as%20stated%20in%20the%20law%3F%20Or%20would%20it%20be%20also%20open%20to%20see%20whether%20that%20procedure%20is%20fair%20or%20not%3F%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20read%20quote%20unquote%20'expression'%20due%20process%20in%20that%20particular%20Article%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Lalit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20us%20some%20time%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20accept%20that%20and%20in%20Maneka%20Gandhi%2C%20we%20came%20up%20with%20what%20is%20called%20the%20expanded%20definition%20of%20right%20to%20life.%20It%20is%20that%20expanded%20definition%20of%20right%20to%20life%2C%20which%20was%20responsible%20for%20our%20reading%20of%20a%20typical%20right%20flowing%20from%20Article%2021.%20That%20is%20to%20say%20that%20every%20child%20in%20this%20country%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%206%20to%2014%20will%20have%20a%20fundamental%20right%20to%20be%20educated%20and%20to%20be%20imparted%20free%2C%20compulsory%20and%20good%20quality%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stated%20in%201993.%20So%2C%20therefore%2C%20in%20about%20nine%20years%20time%2C%20the%20parliament%20came%20out%20with%20an%20amendment%20and%20Article%2021%20capital%20A%20got%20inserted.%20So%2C%20these%20kinds%20of%20developments%20always%20augur%20very%20well%20that%20change%20is%20something%20which%20we%20always%20aspire%20for%2C%20change%20for%20the%20betterment%2C%20change%20for%20the%20better%20lives%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20therefore%2C%20if%20you%20study%20the%20Constitution%2C%20we%20have%20lost%20one%20fundamental%20right%2C%20which%20is%20the%20right%20to%20property.%20But%20we%20gained%20one%20fundamental%20right%2C%20which%20is%20the%20right%20of%20every%20child%20in%20this%20country%20to%20have%20free%20and%20compulsory%20education.%20Have%20we%20really%20lost%20on%20account%20of%20that%20right%20to%20property%20not%20being%20in%20Part%203%3F%20Nothing%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20not%20changed%20the%20spectrum%20so%20far%20as%20the%20entire%20population%20or%20the%20general%20people%20are%20concerned.%20But%20right%20to%20life%20getting%20inserted%20in%20Part%203%2C%20it%20definitely%20has%20had%20a%20tremendous%20dimension%20so%20far%20as%20the%20development%20of%20this%20country%20is%20concerned%2C%20giving%20substance%20to%20everybody's%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Lalit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20at%20least%20two%20generations%20of%20students%20have%20passed%20out%20with%20the%20help%20of%20that%20kind%20of%20facility%20afforded%20by%20that%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20are%20definitely%20moving%20towards%20betterment%2C%20moving%20towards%20good%20ideas%20getting%20inserted%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%20some%20of%20the%20fabulous%20ideas%20getting%20incorporated%20through%20interpretative%20process%20and%20even%20now%20amendments%20as%20well.%20Now%2C%20the%20last%20amendment%2C%20which%20is%20the%20106th%20amendment%2C%20gives%20women%20one%20third%20of%20the%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20in%20every%20state%20legislature%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Lalit%20said%2C%20adding%20we%20are%20moving%20towards%20what%20are%20called%20inclusive%20ideas%20on%20every%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20if%20you%20actually%20look%20at%20the%20substantive%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20there%20are%20very%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20come%20up%20to%20level%20of%20106%20amendments.%20Four%20new%20areas%20got%20included%20in%20the%20Union%20like%20Dadra%20Nagar%20Haveli%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20Gyanam%20Karaikal%2C%20then%20Goa%2C%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20and%20finally%20Sikkim.%20So%2C%20therefore%2C%20some%20of%20these%20amendments%20are%20more%20or%20less%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20procedural%20part%2C%20nothing%20substantive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubstantive%20amendments%2C%20if%20you%20put%20your%20fingers%20on%2C%20there%20may%20be%20just%20about%20seven%20to%20eight%20substantive%20amendments.%20So%2C%20therefore%2C%20otherwise%20every%20amendment%20has%2C%20there%20have%20been%20results%20as%20a%20perhaps%2C%20I%20think%2C%20response%20towards%20some%20of%20the%20judgments%20given%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Say%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Indira%20Sani%20said%20that%20no%20reservation%20in%20promotion%2C%20there%20was%20one%20amendment%20was%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20debate%20whether%20it%20is%20consequential%20seniority%20or%20the%20original%20seniority.%20So%2C%20therefore%2C%20one%20more%20amendment%20came%20into%20effect.%20Then%20another%20amendment%20whether%20backlog%20vacancies%20can%20be%20filled%20in%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20therefore%2C%20these%20are%20som