ly%20Crash%2C%20Shows%20CCTV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20occurred%20on%20Monday%2C%20at%20around%209%3A30%20pm%2C%20after%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Electric%20Supply%20and%20Transport%20(BEST)%20bus%20driver%20in%20Mumbai%20lost%20control%20of%20the%20electric%20bus%20and%20rammed%20into%20vehicles%20and%20pedestrians.%20The%20accident%20claimed%20seven%20lives%2C%20leaving%2042%20others%20injured.%20Over%2020%20vehicles%20were%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20CCTV%20video%2C%20Sanjay%20More%2C%20the%20bus%20driver%2C%20is%20seen%20collecting%20two%20backpacks%20and%20jumping%20out%20of%20a%20broken%20window%20following%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20More%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder.%20He%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20police%20custody%20till%20December%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20Mr%20More%20said%20he%20had%20no%20experience%20driving%20electric%20vehicles.%20He%20was%20given%20only%20a%20day%20of%20training%20during%20which%20he%20drove%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20thrice%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Police%20have%20recorded%20the%20statements%20of%2025%20people%2C%20including%20the%20bus%20conductor.%20Interrogation%20is%20on.%20The%20electric%20bus%20will%20also%20be%20checked%20for%20any%20technical%20faults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmumbai-kurla-best-bus-accident-driver-sanjay-more-had-no-experience-in-driving-electric-bus-say-sources-7229421%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%20Crash%20Driver%20Had%20No%20Experience%20In%20Driving%20Electric%20Bus%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734005160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Flu6sb3jg_mumbai-bus-accident_625x300_12_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fmumbai-kurla-best-bus-a