%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zinzore%20said%20he%20had%20heard%20that%20More%20pressed%20the%20accelerator%20by%20mistake.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20driving%20at%2060%20kmph.%20There%20are%20display%20screens%20and%20an%20all-round%20camera%20view.%20Everything%20can%20be%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20trained%20for%20three%20weeks%20before%20he%20drove%20electric%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F6f72u9e8_bus-crash_625x300_12_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContract%20Drivers'%20Problems%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20contract%20driver%20said%20that%20they%20received%20Rs%2021%2C000%20a%20month%20after%20deductions.%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20drivers%20opt%20for%20double%20shifts%2C%20meaning%20they%20are%20driving%2016%20hours%20a%20day.%20When%20buses%20don't%20stop%2C%20people%20run%20and%20jump%20onto%20them.%20They%20don't%20listen%20to%20the%20drivers%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20leader%20Shashank%20Rao%20said%20he%20does%20not%20consider%20the%20Kurla%20crash%20only%20the%20driver's%20mistake.%20%26quot%3BCatch%20the%20contactor%2C%20they%20are%20working%20double%20shifts%2C%20the%20pay%20is%20not%20good%2C%20remove%20the%20contract%20system%2C%20nobody%20is%20taking%20responsibility.%20Even%20if%20the%20driver%20says%20the%20bus%20has%20a%20mechanical%20problem%2C%20the%20contractor%20gives%20a%20go-ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20BEST%20Hiring%20On%20Contract%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20question%20then%20is%20why%20BEST%20is%20hiring%20drivers%20on%20contract.%20The%20answer%20lies%20in%20BEST's%20growing%20financial%20problems.%20The%20state-run%20bus%20service%20has%20a%20debt%20of%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%20and%20relies%20on%20contract%20staff%20to%20cut%20costs.%20Of%20the%207%2C212%20drivers%20BEST%20has%20now%2C%20only%20649%20--%20about%209%20per%20cent%20--%20are%20permanent.%20Out%20of%20its%202%2C903%20vehicles%2C%201%2C900%20are%20on%20contract.%20Out%20of%20the%201%2C003%20buses%20it%20owns%2C%20750%20will%20be%20scrapped%20in%20the%20next%20nine%20months.%20The%20company%20now%20needs%20an%20urgent%20infusion%20of%20funds.%20BEST%20has%20now%20urged%20BMC%20for%20an%20urgent%20assistance%20of%20Rs%202%2C132%20crore.%20Of%20the%20buses%20BEST%20has%20taken%20on%20lease%2C%20711%20are%20electric%20vehicles%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20pollution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2032%20lakh%20people%20board%20BEST%20buses%20daily%20but%20the%20service%20is%20reeling%20under%20poor%20frequency.%20Is%20hiking%20fares%20a%20solution%20for%20BEST's%20problems%3F%20BEST%20public%20relations%20officer%20Sudas%20Sawant%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20considered%20hiking%20fares%2C%20but%20unless%20we%20bring%20new%20buses%2C%20people%20won't%20take%20it%20well.%20So%20we%20have%20to%20increase%20the%20bus%20frequency%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERTI%20activist%20Jeetendra%20Ghatge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20fare%20should%20not%20be%20hiked.%20See%20the%20bus%20service%20in%20Delhi%20and%20women%20there%20travel%20for%20free.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fae144ep_bus-crash_625x300_12_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurla%20Crash%20A%20Blot%20For%20BEST%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20local%20trains%2C%20BEST%20buses%20are%20considered%20a%20lifeline%20for%20Mumbaikars%20travelling%20far%20f