Fkurla-bus-crash-best-funds-crunch-to-contract-staff-mumbai-bus-crash-spotlights-crippled-best-7232463%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Makes%20Bold%20Claim%2C%20Says%20Bill%20Gates%20Could%20Go%20Bankrupt%20Over%20This%20Reason%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%2C%20is%20known%20for%20making%20headlines%20with%20his%20social%20media%20statements.%20In%20a%20recent%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20made%20a%20bold%20claim%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20Tesla%20becomes%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%2C%20even%20billionaire%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Microsoft%2C%20could%20potentially%20go%20bankrupt.%C2%A0The%20statement%20has%20reignited%20the%20long-standing%20feud%20between%20Musk%20and%20Gates.%20The%20conflict%20dates%20back%20to%202022%20when%20Gates%20allegedly%20suffered%20a%20significant%20loss%20of%20%241.5%20billion%20due%20to%20his%20short%20position%20on%20Tesla's%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Tesla%20does%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20by%20far%2C%20that%20short%20position%20will%20bankrupt%20even%20Bill%20Gates.%26quot%3B%20Musk's%20statement%20was%20a%20response%20to%20an%20X%20user%2C%20Teslaconomics%2C%20who%20shared%20an%20old%20tweet%20from%20him.%20In%20the%202023%20tweet%2C%20the%20CEO%20stated%20that%20taking%20a%20short%20position%20against%20Tesla%2C%20as%20Bill%20Gates%20did%2C%20would%20only%20yield%20the%20highest%20return%20if%20Tesla%20were%20to%20go%20bankrupt.%20Musk%20also%20claimed%20Gates%20had%20placed%20a%20massive%20bet%20on%20Tesla's%20demise%20during%20a%20vulnerable%20period%20for%20the%20company.%20He%20further%20asserted%20that%20such%20a%20large%20short%20position%20can%20drive%20the%20stock%20price%20down%2C%20affecting%20everyday%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20Gates%20*still*%20has%20that%20massive%20bet%20against%20Tesla%20on%20the%20table.%20Someone%20should%20ask%20him%20if%20he%20does.%20The%20lack%20of%20self-awareness%20and%20hypocrisy%20of%20Gates%20who%20had%20the%20nerve%20to%20ask%20me%20to%20donate%20to%20his%20mostly%20window-dressing%20environmental%20causes%2C%20while%20simultaneously%20aiming%20to%20make%20%24500M%20from%20Tesla's%20demise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tweet%20read%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIf%20Tesla%20does%20become%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20by%20far%2C%20that%20short%20position%20will%20bankrupt%20even%20Bill%20Gates%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1866373389528826058%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20investment%20during%20a%202021%20CNBC%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-v9y%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2021%2F02%2F18%2Fbill-gates-tesla-elon-musk-green-economy.html%5C%22%20data-rapid_p%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%20data-ylk%3D%5C%22slk%3Ainterview%3Belm%3Acontext_link%3Bitc%3A0%3Bsec%3Acontent-canvas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Gates%20chose%20not%20to%20comment%20on%20his%20positions%20but%20instead%20praised%20Tesla's%20achievements%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Elon's%20done%20with%20Tesla%20is%20fantastic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20short%20position%20is%20a%20stock%20market%20strategy%20where%20an%20investor%20borrows%20shares%20they%20don't%20own%2C%20sells%20them%20at%20the%20current%20price%2C%20and%20then%20aims%20to%20buy%20them%20back%20later%20at%20a%20lower%20price.%20The%20investor%20profits