n%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Abhay%20has%20planted%20approximately%201%2C27%2C000%20trees%20in%20different%20villages%20in%20Satara%20district.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20villages%20were%20initially%20sceptical%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20water%20conservation%2C%20uncertain%20if%20the%20methods%20would%20work%20in%20their%20own%20communities.%20To%20earn%20their%20trust%2C%20Abhay%20chose%20to%20lead%20by%20example.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20the%20best%20way%20to%20convince%20them%20was%20to%20show%20them%20the%20results%20in%20Dahiwadi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20invited%20them%20to%20visit%2C%20let%20them%20see%20the%20impact%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20allowed%20the%20work%20to%20speak.%E2%80%9D%20Abhay%20was%20able%20to%20turn%20scepticism%20into%20belief%2C%20gradually%20inspiring%20others%20to%20join%20his%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20remarkable%20success%20stories%20came%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Pingali-Kd%2C%20located%20just%20five%20kilometres%20from%20Dahiwadi.%20Initially%2C%20the%20village%20showed%20little%20interest%20in%20Abhay%E2%80%99s%20water%20conservation%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20only%208-10%20people%20were%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhay%20recalls.%20But%20instead%20of%20giving%20up%2C%20Abhay%20invited%2025%20children%20with%20disabilities%20to%20participate%20in%20rallies%2C%20focusing%20on%20Shramdaan%20(labour%20donation).%20These%20rallies%20soon%20captured%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20entire%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%20Sujata%20Waghmare%2C%20admits%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20first%20introduced%20the%20water%20conservation%20project%20in%20our%20village%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20interested.%20But%20when%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20attend%20the%20training%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20The%20training%20was%20so%20impactful%20that%20I%20immediately%20realised%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20brought%20so%20much%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm%20to%20the%20project%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20his%20village.%20His%20passion%20motivated%20me%20to%20get%20actively%20involved%2C%20attending%20meetings%20and%20joining%20the%20projects.%20I%20also%20encouraged%20others%20to%20take%20part%20so%20they%20could%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20water%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20amazed%20me%20most%20was%20that%20even%20though%20Abhay%20sir%20is%20physically%20disabled%2C%20his%20drive%20to%20work%20is%20beyond%20inspiring%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20villagers%20became%20engaged%2C%20Pingali-Kd%20raised%20the%20necessary%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247233%2Fbori-bandh-check-dam-ajay-sharma-sewa-welfare-society-khunti-jharkhand-water-shortage-water-conservation-agriculture-volunteer-work-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efunds%20to%20build%20dams%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20the%20village%20overcame%20its%20water%20scarcity%20issues%2C%20and%20even%20began%20supplying%20water%20to%20neighbouring%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBapu%20Kambale%20from%20Pingali-Kd%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20mechanic%2C%20and%20I%20know%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20Art%20of%20Living%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Water%20conservation%20has%20always%20been%20close%20to%20my%20heart%2C%20as%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20the%20devastating%20effects%20of%20drought.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20we%20had%20to%20walk%20up%20to%20seven%20kilometres%20just%20to%20fetch%20water.%20Our%20wells%20were%20dry%2C%20and%20finding%20drinking%20water%20was%20a%20constant%20struggle.%20With%20such%20a%20shortage%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20think%20of%20farming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20began%20his%20work%20on%20water%20conservation%20in%20our%20village%2C%20I%20joined%20him.%20We%20built%20dams%2C%20and%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20raising%20funds.%20He%20stayed%20in%20our%20village%20for%20nearly%2040%20days%2C%20overseeing%20the%20progress%20and%20ensuring%20everything%20was%20done%20properly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20deep%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20boy%20diagnosed%20with%20polio%20to%20a%20man%20leading%20a%20movement%20for%20water%20conservation%20across%20villages%2C%20Abhay%20Todkar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20source%20of%20hope%20for%20others%20facing%20similar%20challenges.%20His%20story%20proves%20that%20no%20limitation%20can%20hold%20back%20the%20human%20spirit%20when%20fuelled%20by%20grit%20and%20a%20passion%20for%20serving%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Abhay%20Todkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733754600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-01-at-22.12.46-1-1733487498.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387316%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhay%20Todkar%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20from%20drought-prone%20Dahiwadi%20village%20defied%20the%20odds%20of%20living%20with%20polio%20to%20lead%20a%20remarkable%20water%20conservation%20movement.%20His%20efforts%20have%20brought%20sustainable%20change%20to%2064%20villages%2C%20turning%20struggles%20into%20triumphs%20through%20determination%20and%20community-driven%20initiatives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387316%2Fabhay-todkar-dahiwadi-polio-water-conservation-movement-across-villages-maharashtra%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Magazine%20Is%20Challenging%20What%20It%20Means%20To%20Be%20a%20Child%20Born%20in%20a%20Red-Light%20Area%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20little%20and%20the%20police%20would%20raid%20our%20houses%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20see%20people%20jumping%20over%20walls%20and%20running%20away.%20My%20grandmother%20would%20wake%20up%20all%20the%20children%20in%20the%20house%2C%20gather%20us%20together%2C%20and%20tell%20us%20to%20read%20out%20loud%2C%20so%20the%20police%20would%20know%20that%20school-going%2C%20regular%20children%20lived%20there.%20I%20always%20found%20this%20so%20strange.%20Why%20were%20we%20constantly%20told%20to%20hide%2C%20to%20run%3F%20What%20crime%20had%20we%20committed%20that%20made%20us%20feel%20that%20our%20existence%20was%20dishonest%3F%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Naseema%20Khatoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%2C%2039%2C%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20red-light%20area%2C%20experiencing%20firsthand%20the%20stigma%20and%20neglect%20faced%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350204%2Fsandhya-nair-kranti-ngo-daughters-of-sex-workers-kamathipura-international-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esex%20workers%20and%20their%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20having%20broken%20free%20from%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%2C%20she%20has%20become%20a%20powerful%20voice%20for%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20was%20enrolled%20in%20school%20that%20I%20developed%20a%20sense%20of%20inquisitiveness%20about%20my%20identity.%20I%20would%20be%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20people%20would%20ask%20me%20my%20full%20name%20and%20where%20I%20was%20from.%20But%20I%20was%20told%20not%20to%20tell%20people%20where%20I%20lived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20a%20red-light%20district%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseema%E2%80%99s%20home%20was%20Chaturbhuj%20Sthan%2C%20a%20red-light%20district%20in%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bihar.%20Named%20after%20a%20Vishnu%20temple%2C%20the%20area%20has%20historically%20been%20home%20to%20sex%20workers%20and%20%3Cem%3Etawaifs%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20its%20religious%20name%20does%20not%20shield%20the%20community%20from%20societal%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20not%20tell%20people%20who%20I%20am%20and%20where%20I%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%20Naseema%20remembers%20asking%20her%20father%2C%20who%20quickly%20shut%20her%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20girls%20from%20school%20would%20all%20walk%20home%20together%2C%20but%20they%20would%20take%20a%20long%20wounded%20route%20to%20avoid%20my%20%3Cem%3Egully%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20were%20told%20to%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99d%20go%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Naseema%20was%20a%20witness%20to%20frequent%20police%20raids%20in%20her%20neighbourhood.%20These%20experiences%20left%20a%20lasting%20impact%2C%20and%20it%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20she%20began%20to%20fully%20understand%20the%20marginalisation%20her%20community%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fjugnu1-1733397818-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20Naseema%20Khatoon%20who%20is%20a%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20a%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20(NHRC)%20advisory%20group%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5