0great%20pillar%20of%20support%20throughout%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manikanta.%20While%20the%20processing%20of%20products%20takes%20place%20at%20their%20facility%20in%20the%20village%2C%20the%20packaging%20and%20delivery%20operations%20are%20managed%20at%20their%20store%20in%20Guntur%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20transition%20from%20production%20to%20customer.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20Pavani%20and%20I%20take%20care%20of%20the%20packing%20and%20delivery%20personally%2C%20ensuring%20everything%20is%20in%20line%20with%20our%20commitment%20to%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20in%20knowing%20that%20the%20food%20we%20create%20is%20improving%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%20and%20the%20positive%20feedback%20we%20receive%20each%20day%20keeps%20me%20inspired%20to%20keep%20doing%20better.%20Working%20with%20Sreshte%20has%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20me%2C%20it%20has%20not%20only%20kept%20me%20active%20but%20has%20also%20improved%20my%20own%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subbarao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20years%20of%20persistence%2C%20the%20couple%20proudly%20opened%20their%20first%20official%20Sreshte%20store%20in%20Guntur%20in%202019%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241026-WA0034-1_11zon-1733381439-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c