2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20farmers%20and%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20extends%20not%20only%20to%20their%20customers%20but%20also%20to%20their%20community.%20Sreshte%20currently%20collaborates%20with%2055%20farmers%2C%20empowering%20them%20with%20fair%20prices%20and%20stable%20markets%20for%20their%20produce.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20employ%2010%20dedicated%20staff%20members%20who%20assist%20with%20packaging%20and%20delivery%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20local%20economy%20and%20providing%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESesha%20Rao%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Guntur%20district%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20grateful%20to%20work%20with%20Sreshte%2C%20as%20they%20ensure%20I%20receive%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20my%20natural%20farming%20practices%20with%20chillies.%20Their%20support%20has%20not%20only%20encouraged%20me%20to%20continue%20with%20organic%20farming%2C%20but%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20grow%20professionally%20by%20enabling%20me%20to%20sell%20my%20chillies%20and%20chilli%20powder%20directly%20to%20customers.%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20continuing%20this%20path%20and%20am%20proud%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20organic%20farming%20community%20with%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20measure%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20success%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20stories%20of%20its%20customers.%20Nandana%2C%20a%20regular%20shopper%20from%20Rajendranagar%2C%20Guntur%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20prefer%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20organic%20foods%20because%20they%20are%20free%20from%20harmful%20chemicals%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20artificial%20additives.%20I%20can%20taste%20the%20difference%2C%20the%20food%20is%20fresh%20and%20the%20natural%20flavours%20are%20distinctive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%2