es%20that%20farmers%20can%20sell%20their%20produce%20at%20premium%20prices%20by%20providing%20better%20market%20access%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20store%20supports%20local%20farmers%20and%20uses%20eco-friendly%20packaging%2C%20which%20is%20in%20line%20with%20my%20values%20of%20sustainability%20and%20ethical%20consumption.%20Shopping%20here%20has%20not%20only%20improved%20my%20health%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20also%20contributing%20to%20a%20better%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManikanta%20and%20Pavani%20have%20big%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20They%E2%80%99re%20looking%20to%20expand%20their%20processing%20unit%20and%20continue%20building%20partnerships%20with%20more%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9COur%20dream%20is%20to%20take%20Sreshte%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20offering%20organic%20products%20to%20more%20people%20and%20supporting%20more%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pavani.%20Their%20next%20step%20is%20to%20launch%20an%20online%20store%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20reach%20a%20wider%20audience%20and%20make%20their%20products%20even%20more%20accessible.%20For%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20believed%20that%20offline%20selling%20was%20crucial%20for%20building%20strong%20relationships%20with%20customers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20our%20customers%20loved%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pavani.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20feedback%20helps%20us%20improve%20everything%2C%20from%20packaging%20to%20storage%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20always%20striving%20to%20be%20as%20transparent%20as%20possible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20Sreshte%20is%20not%20just%20about%20running%20a%20business%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20building%20a%20deeper%20connection%20to%20the%20food%20people%20consume.%20Their%20commitment%20to%20providing%20healthier%2C%20organic%20options%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20dedication%20to%20educating%20customers%20on%20wh