itous%2C%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20limited%20options%20for%20modifying%20the%20existing%20walls%2C%20and%20OSB%20proved%20invaluable%20due%20to%20its%20easy%20and%20quick%20installation%20system.%E2%80%9D%20What%20the%20team%20also%20discovered%20during%20the%20project%2C%20was%20that%20the%20material%20boasted%20excellent%20acoustical%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orient%20stranded%20boards%20are%20a%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin%2C%20they%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOrient%20stranded%20boards%20are%20a%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin.%20They%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Edifice%20Consultant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20OSB%20wall%20panels%20helped%20us%20nullify%20the%20unwanted%20refraction%20and%20reverberation%20in%20the%20studio.%20Since%20the%20OSB%20panels%20are%20not%20as%20highly%20compressed%20as%20plywood%20they%20are%20excellent%20sound%20absorbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aameer%20adds.%20But%20the%20real%20magic%20lies%20in%20the%20matrix.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20raw%20finish%20of%20%5BOSB%E2%80%99s%5D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20strand%20composition%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds%20a%20subtle%20texture%20to%20the%20overall%20monochromatic%2C%20industrial-themed%20office%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20OSB%20does%20manage%20to%20lend%20some%20bespoke%20detailing%20to%20the%20building%2C%20it%20is%20susceptible%20to%20moisture%20absorption.%20This%2C%20says%20Aameer%2C%20can%20affect%20its%20dimensional%20stability%20and%20performance%20over%20time.%20Another%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20since%20OSB%20is%20procured%20from%20trees%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverify%20the%20specific%20environmental%20certifications%20and%20sustainability%20attributes%20of%20the%20OSB%20product%20being%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Compressed%20Stabilised%20Earth%20Bricks%20(CSEB)%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20study%20underscored%2C%20%E2%80%9CCompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%20due%20to%20the%20lower%20amount%20of%20energy%20required%20for%20their%20production%2C%20lower%20cost%20and%20lower%20carbon%20footprint.%20Compared%20to%20cement%20concrete%2C%20CSEBs%20also%20require%20less%20embodied%20energy%2C%20with%20some%20authors%20indicating%20that%20only%20one%20percent%20of%20the%20production%20energy%20of%20cement%20concrete%20is%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20architects%20Rahul%20Kadri%2C%20Nithin%20Hosabettu%2C%20Sahil%20Bipin%20Deshpande%2C%20Viraj%20Naralkar%2C%20and%20Aakash%20Shrivastav%20of%20Mumbai-based%20IMK%20Architects%20were%20tasked%20with%20designing%20the%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%2C%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312182%2Fmaking-of-odisha-krushi-bhavan-sustainable-architecture-local-craftsmanship%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20were%20enthusiastic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20discovered%2C%20not%20only%20do%20the%20bricks%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20structure%20but%20they%20also%20boast%2080%20percent%20less%20energy%20consumption%20while%20achieving%20thermal%20comfort.%20The%20architects%20share%20that%20the%20bricks%20they%20used%20were%20made%20using%20a%20natural%20mix%20of%20red%20soil%2C%20sand%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crumbled%20rock)%20stabilised%20with%20five%20percent%20cement.%20This%20ensured%20their%20durability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%20has%20been%20built%20with%20compressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20that%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1733298121-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20SUHRC%20Symbiosis%20University%20Hospital%20and%20Research%20Centre%2C%20Lavale%2C%20Pune%20has%20been%20built%20with%20compressed%20stabilised%20earth%20bricks%20(CSEBs)%20that%20are%20good%20candidates%20to%20replace%20fired%20bricks%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20IMK%20Architects%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20extend%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20scope%20of%20sustainability%2C%20the%20architects%20ensured%20that%20the%20bricks%20were%20made%20on-site%20by%20using%20a%20block-making%20machine%2C%20thus%20cutting%20the%20emission%20of%20carbon%2C%20while%20also%20employing%20local%20labour%20to%20sun%20dry%20instead%20of%20kiln-fire%20the%20bricks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20all%20soils%20may%20be%20suitable%20for%20CSEB.%20Avoid%20using%20topsoil%20and%20organic%20soils.%20The%20type%20of%20stabiliser%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20mix%20will%20depend%20upon%20the%20soil%20in%20question.%20Cement%20works%20best%20for%20sandy%20soils%2C%20while%20lime%20works%20best%20for%20clayey%20soils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Acetylated%20wood%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWood%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305212%2Feco-friendly-sustainable-house-in-thrissur-kerala-using-bamboo-bricks-wood-red-oxide-saves-electricity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstruction%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20draws%20concerns%20for%20its%20responsiveness%20to%20environmental%20variables.%20So%2C%20imagine%20a%20variety%20of%20wood%20that%20performs%20well%20irrespective%20of%20the%20surroundings%3B%20one%20that%20can%20tolerate%20extreme%20temperatures%20as%20well%20as%20endure%20water%20exposure!%20When%20architect%20Vijay%20Dahiya%2C%20partner%20at%20team3%2C%20discovered%20acetylated%20wood%2C%20he%20was%20excited%20to%20try%20it%20out%20in%20one%20of%20his%20projects%2C%20%E2%80%98Mehra%20Residence%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mehra%20Residence%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20constructed%20using%20acetylated%20wood%20which%20lends%20anti-fungal%20properties%20to%20the%20structure%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vijay%20Dahiya%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-5_11zon-1733298312-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386136%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2